kind: llman.sdd.spec
name: "cursor-export"
purpose: "Describe Cursor export selection and output behavior (interactive and non-interactive)."
valid_scope[4]: src/x/cursor/command.rs,src/x/cursor/database.rs,src/x/cursor/models.rs,"llmanspec/specs/cursor-export/"
requirements[8]{req_id,title,statement}:
  r1,"Non-interactive database selection order","Non-interactive cursor export MUST honor `db_path` first, then `workspace_dir` resolution, then auto-discovery when neither is provided. Auto-discovery selects the latest workspace database, preferring a database that contains chat/composer data."
  r2,"Non-interactive selection defaults","When `composer_id` is provided, the export MUST target only that composer conversation; otherwise it MUST export all conversations from the resolved database."
  r3,Output mode validation,"`output_mode` MUST be one of `console`, `file`, or `single-file` (default `console`). Unsupported values MUST return an error instead of printing and continuing."
  r4,File output location rules,"File-based output modes MUST follow deterministic output locations and naming."
  r5,交互选择必须使用稳定对话标识符,交互式 cursor export MUST 将用户选择映射到稳定的对话标识符（例如：composer 使用 `composer_id`，传统聊天使用 `tab_id`）。导出结果 MUST 与被选择的标识符集合一致，而不是依赖展示 index。
  r6,搜索选择必须共享同一标识符空间,交互搜索结果 MUST 返回与主列表相同的稳定标识符。导出 MUST 将搜索选择与主列表选择以一致方式处理（可合并、可去重，不得混用不同 index 空间）。
  r7,交互导出不得加载未选中对话的完整内容,交互式 cursor export MUST 避免为未选中对话加载完整内容（尤其是 composer bubbles 等重数据），只为被选中项加载必要数据。
  r8,SQLite 连接线程安全,cursor export 打开 SQLite 数据库时 MUST 使用 `SQLITE_OPEN_FULL_MUTEX`（或线程安全的等价标志），MUST NOT 使用 `SQLITE_OPEN_NO_MUTEX`。当且仅当通过安全分析确认连接仅在单线程使用且未来不会跨线程时，可保留 `SQLITE_OPEN_NO_MUTEX` 但 MUST 添加代码注释说明理由与约束条件。
scenarios[13]{req_id,id,given,when,then}:
  r1,"db-path-provided","","`db_path` is set in non-interactive mode",the export uses that database path directly
  r1,"workspace-dir-provided","",`workspace_dir` is set and `db_path` is not provided,the export resolves the workspace to its database path and uses it
  r1,"no-overrides","",neither `db_path` nor `workspace_dir` is provided,"the export selects a database path via auto-discovery"
  r2,"composer-id-provided","","`composer_id` is set in non-interactive mode",the export writes only the matching composer conversation or returns an error if not found
  r2,"no-composer-id","","`composer_id` is not provided in non-interactive mode",the export writes all available conversations
  r3,"unsupported-output-mode","",`output_mode` is not one of the supported values,the command returns an error that is surfaced by the CLI entrypoint
  r4,"output-mode-single-file","","`output_mode` is `single-file`","the export writes to `output_file` if provided, otherwise defaults to `cursor_conversations.md`"
  r4,"output-mode-file","",`output_mode` is `file`,"the export writes into the `output_file` directory if provided, otherwise defaults to `./cursor_exports`"
  r5,排序展示不影响导出正确性,"",交互 UI 展示的是排序后的对话列表，用户选择了 A 与 B,即使底层存储顺序不同，导出也只包含 A 与 B
  r6,搜索选择导出正确,"",用户通过 “search more” 流程选择了若干对话,导出结果与搜索选择完全一致
  r7,大库仅选少量对话,"",workspace 中存在大量对话但用户只选择少量导出,导出仅为被选中对话加载完整内容
  r8,"full-mutex-used",cursor export 打开数据库,SQLite 连接创建,使用 FULL_MUTEX（或在注释中明确说明 NO_MUTEX 为单线程安全）
  r8,"export-works",数据库可正常打开,cursor export 执行导出,功能正常，无退化
